### 4. Drug–Target Interaction (ChEMBL)
- **Used in:** Chapter 9
- **Source:** [ChEMBL Database](https://www.ebi.ac.uk/chembl/)
- **Description:** Bioactivity data linking compounds to biological targets
- **License:** Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 3.0
- **Download:** See `Ch09_Decision_Support/chembl_query.ipynb`

