### 5. Diabetes Clinical Dataset (PIMA Indians)
- **Used in:** Chapters 5, 9
- **Source:** [Kaggle](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/uciml/pima-indians-diabetes-database) (CC0 Public Domain)
